When we include the line:
frc::DigitalOutput limitSwitch{9};
and then deploy it, the deploy is successful but our Driver Station gives us a no robot code error. When we comment out just this line, we no longer have the problem, but we want to be able to use the limit switch. We even tried deleting every other line besides essentials to run the robot and that line, and we still got the no robot code error. We also tried connecting to another roboRIO, and we got the same results.

We’ve tried everything we can think of and cannot find this problem anywhere else online.
